# Neo Drive UI Rules

Apply when editing drive layout, dashboard, or explorer. Match the **Ospyn Neo My Drive** design system.

## Design Tokens (`.drive-shell` in `app/globals.css`)

| Token | Value / usage |
|-------|----------------|
| `--drive-surface` | `#f9fafb` — main content background |
| `--drive-quick-access` | `#f2f4f7` — quick access card fill |
| `--drive-link` | `#008542` — “View more”, upgrade links |
| `--drive-search-bg` | `#eef4fb` — header search (`.drive-search-input`) |
| Sidebar (light) | White sidebar via `:root:not(.dark):not(.semi-dark) .drive-shell` |
| Sidebar (dark / semi-dark) | `#0b121e` via `.dark .drive-shell` / `.semi-dark .drive-shell` |
| Active nav | `--sidebar-accent` / `--sidebar-accent-foreground` (green on dark) |

Use utility classes: `drive-main`, `drive-quick-access-card`, `drive-link`, `drive-search-input`.

## Typography (see `docs/TYPOGRAPHY_GUIDE.md`)

- Page greeting: `text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight`
- Section titles: `text-base font-semibold`
- Nav / body: `text-sm`; meta: `text-xs text-muted-foreground`

## Sidebar (`AppSidebar`)

- Logo block: green “O” tile + `productName` (small) + `driveName` (bold)
- **WORKSPACE** label + `workspaceName` button with gem icon
- Main nav from `getSidebarNavItems()`; active = green accent on dark
- **Settings** above storage widget (not in main list)
- Storage: progress + “Upgrade Storage” (`appConfig.storageUsedGb` / `storageTotalGb`)

## Header (`DocumentsAppHeader`)

- Left: `SidebarTrigger` + page title from `ROUTE_TITLES` / active nav
- Center: pill search — placeholder **“Search in Neo Drive”**, Clear when typing
- Right: Sparkles, Bell (red dot), **Palette** (opens `ThemeManager` sheet), user avatar + name/email from `appConfig`

Do not add upload CTA to header; **+ New** belongs on file explorer toolbar only. Theme controls: navbar Palette icon or Settings page.

## Dashboard (`DriveDashboardPage`)

- `QuickAccessSection`: 2×5 grid (`xl:grid-cols-5`), cards 60px tall, `#f2f4f7`
- Folder icon: blue folder + centered white star (`QuickAccessItemIcon`)
- Files: blue “W” tile (docx), red “PDF” tile
- `Recent Files`: white bordered cards, preview block, optional HR/Finance tag, timestamp footer

## File Explorer (`FileExplorerPage`)

- Breadcrumbs → toolbar (folder search + sort/filter/view + **+ New**) → `FileExplorerTable` embedded in one white card
- Table: use `TableContainer` / `TableSortHead` / `data-state="selected"` per `TABLE_BEHAVIOR_GUIDE.md`

## Do Not

- Reintroduce e-stamp “Upgrade Pro” card in sidebar footer (use storage meter).
- Use `neo-table` / `request-row` for drive file lists.
- Change `(with-header)` `/dashboard` when implementing drive — that is a separate template demo.
